{% schema %}
  {
    
    "name": "Section 3",
    "tag": "section",
    "class": "gps-626145920433521203 gps gpsil",
    "settings": [{"type":"paragraph","content":"Section design by GemPages. [Click here to start design](https://admin.shopify.com/store/ywhwyf-mp/apps/gempages-cro/app/shopify/edit?pageType=GP_STATIC&editorId=626145920215417395&sectionId=626145920433521203)"},{"type":"select","label":"Section Preload","id":"section_preload","options":[{"label":"On","value":"true"},{"label":"Off","value":"false"},{"label":"Off Lazy Script","value":"off_lazy_script"}],"default":"false"},{"type":"text","label":"Checksum","id":"checksum"},{"type":"html","id":"ggua-F7nsHG_text","label":"ggua-F7nsHG_text","default":"The Science Behind <span style=\"color:#8B1638;\">Nifora</span>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggou59l0UOL_text","label":"ggou59l0UOL_text","default":"Reported results from real users and clinical-backed ingredients:"},{"type":"html","id":"ggWaDDckgTA_text","label":"ggWaDDckgTA_text","default":"Improvement in skin firmness after 6 weeks"},{"type":"html","id":"ggXkLqVD6xc_text","label":"ggXkLqVD6xc_text","default":"Reduction in fine lines and wrinkles"},{"type":"html","id":"ggpQ_Fo-hzQ_text","label":"ggpQ_Fo-hzQ_text","default":"Increase in skin hydration with consistent use"},{"type":"html","id":"ggOTG9gcPWM_text","label":"ggOTG9gcPWM_text","default":"Improved elasticity and skin bounce"},{"type":"html","id":"gg3a9NeZtnM_text","label":"gg3a9NeZtnM_text","default":"Not All Masks Are Created Equal. Here’s Why:"},{"type":"html","id":"ggDtawbzOjL_text","label":"ggDtawbzOjL_text","default":"<p>Most masks are made from cotton or paper.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>They’re soaked in liquid that evaporates before your skin can absorb it.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>They barely cling to the skin—and even less of what’s inside reaches beneath the surface.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>That’s not skincare.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>That’s wasted time.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gga_mQnBrNN_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gga_mQnBrNN_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/11_c6699700-3cd8-4281-b887-eb88cb53243f.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggKrZWbIuTz_text","label":"ggKrZWbIuTz_text","default":"<p>Nifora’s hydrogel mask was engineered differently.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>It uses a&nbsp;<strong>structured hydrogel matrix</strong>—a flexible, skin-mimicking material that adheres to your face like a second skin.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>As it warms from your body heat, the gel slowly dissolves—releasing active ingredients over 3–4 hours or overnight.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg-ISWbFDrV_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gg-ISWbFDrV_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/12_1cdad67c-a76c-4721-a1a6-8fd991f06b16.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggj5UqXrNXK_text","label":"ggj5UqXrNXK_text","default":"<p>No rushing. No evaporation.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Just deep, consistent absorption.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>It forms a moisture-sealing barrier that gives the ingredients time to work.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>That’s what makes the difference.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggSv4RCjFZw_text","label":"ggSv4RCjFZw_text","default":"What Happens When You Combine These Actives in One Mask"},{"type":"html","id":"ggGayW_JmhC_text","label":"ggGayW_JmhC_text","default":"<p>Hydrolyzed Collagen</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggVaWsJ3MVH_text","label":"ggVaWsJ3MVH_text","default":"<p>Sinks deep into the skin to stimulate natural collagen renewal—supporting firmer, plumper, and more elastic skin with each use.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggOgqoKZ0bG_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggOgqoKZ0bG_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/Collagen-ing.webp"},{"type":"html","id":"ggjepVdESNm_text","label":"ggjepVdESNm_text","default":"<p>Hyaluronic Acid</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggMG3Eqaldy_text","label":"ggMG3Eqaldy_text","default":"<p>A hydration powerhouse that draws moisture deep into the skin, leaving it visibly plump, dewy, and refreshed.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggSSmbPE25b_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggSSmbPE25b_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/Hyaluronix.webp"},{"type":"html","id":"ggTLKvlVvPk_text","label":"ggTLKvlVvPk_text","default":"<p>Vitamin E</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg_gKnF0QcA_text","label":"gg_gKnF0QcA_text","default":"<p>A potent antioxidant that supports skin repair, smooths texture, and helps protect against environmental damage.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggNBVHgvSjt_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggNBVHgvSjt_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/Vitamin_E.webp"},{"type":"html","id":"ggwm2H7AqiX_text","label":"ggwm2H7AqiX_text","default":"<p>Niacinamide (Vitamin B3)</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggKhQE9FilX_text","label":"ggKhQE9FilX_text","default":"<p>Brightens, balances, and strengthens the skin barrier. Helps reduce redness, dark spots, and signs of fatigue—perfect for stressed or aging skin.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggYHmOQ_mJH_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggYHmOQ_mJH_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/Niacinamide.webp"},{"type":"html","id":"gg5qHSK9wut_text","label":"gg5qHSK9wut_text","default":"<p>Glycerin</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggLt6zqcrEp_text","label":"ggLt6zqcrEp_text","default":"<p>Acts like a moisture magnet, locking in hydration and keeping your skin soft, supple, and resilient all day long.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg2EtK6npwD_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gg2EtK6npwD_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/Glycerin.webp"},{"type":"html","id":"ggxv1X343_v_text","label":"ggxv1X343_v_text","default":"<p>Galactomyces</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg_hJsyKiZK_text","label":"gg_hJsyKiZK_text","default":"<p>A fermented ingredient known for boosting radiance, refining skin texture, and enhancing glow—often used in cult-favorite Korean skincare for a reason.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggcaPo11Q1g_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggcaPo11Q1g_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/Galactomyces.webp"}],
